1970 to 2006¶

In [15]:
df_1970to2006 = pd.read_excel(data+'hhi.xls', converters={'fyear' : float, 'sic3': int,'hhi_full':float,'hhi_segment_check':float, 'hhi_segment':float, 'gvkey_full':int, 'gvkey_segment_check':int, 'gvkey_segment': int, 'nyear': int})
df_1970to2006['constant'] = 1
df_1970to2006 = df_1970to2006.query('1969 < fyear')
df_1970to2006['nyear'] = df_1970to2006['fyear']-1970
df_1970to2006 = df_1970to2006.drop(['hhi_full'], axis = 1)
grouped_1970to2006 = df_1970to2006.groupby('sic3')
In [16]:
lst=[]
for name, group in grouped_1970to2006:
    group = group.dropna()
    y = group[['hhi_segment']]
    x = group[['nyear', 'constant']]
    try: 
        ols = sm.OLS(y.astype(float), x.astype(float)).fit()
        beta= ols.params[-2]
        frame=pd.DataFrame({'sic3':name, 'beta':beta}, index=[0])
        lst.append(frame)
    except:
        pass

seg_1970to2006 = pd.concat(lst)
In [17]:

1975 to 2006¶

In [25]:
df_1975to2006 = pd.read_excel(data+'hhi.xls', converters={'fyear' : float, 'sic3': int,'hhi_full':float,'hhi_segment_check':float, 'hhi_segment':float, 'gvkey_full':int, 'gvkey_segment_check':int, 'gvkey_segment': int, 'nyear': int})
df_1975to2006['constant'] = 1
df_1975to2006 = df_1975to2006.query('1974 < fyear')
df_1975to2006['nyear'] = df_1975to2006['fyear']-1975
df_1975to2006 = df_1975to2006.drop(['hhi_full'], axis = 1)
grouped_1975to2006 = df_1975to2006.groupby('sic3')
In [26]:
lst=[]
for name, group in grouped_1975to2006:
    group = group.dropna()
    y = group[['hhi_segment']]
    x = group[['nyear', 'constant']]
    try: 
        ols = sm.OLS(y.astype(float), x.astype(float)).fit()
        beta= ols.params[-2]
        frame=pd.DataFrame({'sic3':name, 'beta':beta}, index=[0])
        lst.append(frame)
    except:
        pass

seg_1975to2006 = pd.concat(lst)

In [76]:
lst=[]
for name, group in grouped_1995to2006:
    group = group.dropna()
    y = group[['hhi_segment']]
    x = group[['nyear', 'constant']]
    try: 
        ols = sm.OLS(y.astype(float), x.astype(float)).fit()
        beta= ols.params[-2]
        frame=pd.DataFrame({'sic3':name, 'beta':beta}, index=[0])
        lst.append(frame)
    except:
        pass

seg_1995to2006 = pd.concat(lst)
